title: Neil Young - 100 Times Or More(4-CD SBD)2018ak
description:
Neil Young - 100 Times Or More(4-CD SBD)2018ak320

Alright I said I would bring the whole thing featuring some of the best live versions of Neils most often-performed songs. That is, all the songs he has performed at least 100 times or more in concert.  This list is compiled based on data available after the Freedom of Speach Tour of 2006 and after the BSB and Farm Aid 2006 concerts.

Tracklist

Disc 1:
01.All Along The Watchtower (1993-07-03 Torhout Festival, Torhout, Belgium)
02 Country Home (1976-11-15 Auditorium Theater, Chicago, IL (Late Show))
03 Unknown Legend (1992-03-14 Texas Stadium, Irving, TX)
04 Love To Burn (2003-06-13 Bonnaroo Festival, Manchester, TN)
05 Southern Pacific (1984-09-25 Austin City Limits,Austin, TX)
06 I Am A Child (1970-02-25 Music Hall, Cincinnati, OH)
07 Drive Back (1987-06-02 National Exhibition Centre, Birmingham, England)
08 Crime In The City (1989-12-10 Muziektheater Stopera, Amsterdam, Holland)
09 Love And Only Love (2001-01-20 Rock City, Barra da Tijuca, Rio de Janeiro, Brazil)

Disc 2:
01 Tell Me Why (1970-06-04 Fillmore East, New York, NY)
02 Too Far Gone (1976-11-15 Auditorium Theater, Chicago, IL (Late Show))
03 Dont Cry No Tears (1976-11-15 Auditorium Theater, Chicago, IL (Late Show)
04 Everybody Knows This Is Nowhere (1970-02-25 Music Hall, Cincinnati, OH)
05 On The Way Home 2004-09-18 Farm Aid 2004,White River Amphitheatre, Auburn,WA)
06 Dont Be Denied (1974-07-09 Coliseum, Seattle, WA)
07 Dance, Dance, Dance (1971-02-23 BBC TV Studios, London, England)
08 From Hank To Hendrix (1992-11-17 WTTW Studios, Chicago, IL)
09 This Notes For You (1988-08-19 Darien Lake Amphitheater, Darien Lake, NY)
10 Soul Of A Woman (1984-09-25 Austin City Limits,Austin, TX)
11 Are You Ready For The Country? (1984-09-25 Austin City Limits, Austin, TX)
12 Sedan Delivery (2003-06-13 Bonnaroo Festival, Manchester, TN)
13 Cowgirl In The Sand (1974-07-13 Oakland Stadium, Oakland, CA)
14 Fuckin Up (2003-06-13 Bonnaroo Festival, Manchester, TN)
15 The Loner (1970-02-25 Music Hall, Cincinnati, OH)
16 My My, Hey Hey (1989-12-10 Muziektheater Stopera, Amsterdam, Holland)
